item.title: CVE-2019-1010038|2024-08-05T03:07:18.159Z -- openmodelica -- omcompiler
item.description: OpenModelica OMCompiler is affected by: Buffer Overflow. The impact is: Possible code execution and denial of service. The component is: OPENMODELICAHOME parameter changeable via environment variable. The attack vector is: Changing an environment variable.
